oo, and Sprocket!\n\nSUBSCRIBE for new Nick Jr. videos weekly! You can find more of your favorite Nick Jr. shows weekday mornings on Nickelodeon and everywhere you find Nick Jr.!\n\n**ADVERTISEMENT**\n\nYou can watch full episodes online, play games, and discover silly surprises in the free Nick Jr. App and at NickJr.com.\niTunes: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/nick-jr...\nGoogle: https://play.google.com/store/apps/de...\nAmazon: https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B01...\nWeb: http://www.nickjr.com/\n \nStream Nick Jr. for free in the Nick Jr. App on Roku and Apple TV or download full episodes for offline viewing on iTunes or Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/de...\n\nYou can also download premium apps featuring your favorite Nick Jr. shows on iTunes, Google Play, and Amazon: \niTunes: https://apps.apple.com/us/developer/n...\nGoogle Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/de...\nAmazon: https://www.amazon.com/s?rh=n%3A23501...\n\nDownload premium Nick Jr. games and apps on iTunes, Google Play, and Amazon:  \n\nNick Jr. Draw and Play \niPhone: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/nick-jr...\niPad: https://apps.apple.com/us/app/nick-jr...\nAmazon: https://www.amazon.com/Nickelodeon-Ni...\n, Welcome to the OFFICIAL Nick Jr. Music channel, where you can find Nick Jr. songs, compilations, and lyric videos! \n\nJoin all of your favorite Nick Jr. characters from shows like PAW Patrol, Rubble \u0026 Crew, Bubble Guppies, Blaze and the Monster Machines, and Blues Clues \u0026 You! in sing-alongs, nursery rhymes, and classic jams in this hub for all things music!\n\nFrom educational videos to theme songs to videos that make you want to dance, watch Blue, Blaze, Bossy Bear and so many more characters sing your favorite songs! \n\nSubscribe to the Nick Jr. Music YouTube Channel: https://at.nick.com/NickJrMusicSubscribe\nWatch more videos on the Nick Jr. Music YouTube Channel: https://at.nick.com/NickJrMusicChannel\n\n#NickJrMusic #SingAlong #NurseryRhymes","commandRuns":